headline: Tractor Supply Company Raises Dividend; Expands Its Board of Directors With Appointment of Sonia Syngal
summary: BRENTWOOD, Tenn., February 11, 2026--Tractor Supply Company today announced its Board of Directors has increased its dividend and announce the appointment of a new member of its Board.
